info.summary: Twelve CS$$ Maxis-esque commercial shops on 1x1, 1x2 or 1x3 lots.
info.description: These are 1x1 and 1x2 BATs and are mostly on those sized lots (with a few 1x3 sprinkled in). Stats have been modded mostly in keeping with prior uploads, and all are medium wealth stage 1 growable with nightlights and custom queries as well.
